## Namespace convention

All ontologies in this hub use the namespace pattern:

```
https://{company_domain}/ont/<domain>#
```

For example:
- Customer domain → `https://{company_domain}/ont/customer#`
- Order domain → `https://{company_domain}/ont/order#`

